name	desc	weight	object
"Cardboard Box"	"A tattered and battered cardboard box that likely contains your much sought after paws and tail. The poor thing has clearly been put through the wringer as its surface is pitted in thin cuts, scrapes, and covered in stamps both foreign and domestic. While a [']generous['] layer of brown tape has been coiled around to keep the thing from falling apart, how long it will hold together is anyone's guess."	3	Cardboard Box

the scent of Cardboard Box is "The box smells of aging cardboard, glue, and oil.".

Cardboard Box is a grab object.
Usedesc of Cardboard Box is "[FoxyBoxesuse]";

to say FoxyBoxesuse:
	say "     Gleefully tearing into the distressed container, you quickly rip away the frayed bits of cardboard to reveal a half-popped sheet of bubble wrap coiled about your [italic type]cuddly wuggly[roman type] suit's adorable [italic type]pawbs[roman type], and long cute bushy tail secured in a clear vacuum-sealed plastic back. Ripping the paws open first, you're pleasantly surprised to find the fetching orange-furred boots and gloves are made of stretchy nylon that could accommodate all but the largest individuals. A series of noticeably soft, yet durable pads shaped like cute black hearts have been affixed to the soles and palms, though this will undoubtedly make walking on rough terrain... interesting, and make gripping things difficult, a part of you is still looking forward to trying them on. Meanwhile, the silky reddish-orange tail tipped with tapered white streak of fur on its end, seems to be a simple, if classic piece of wearable art, you muse, unfurling the fluffy floor dragger, watching it bounce and wag with the slightest provocation. Turning it over in your hands, you find a simple little band bundled along its base, much like the paws, this thin strip of fabric could easily fit most pre-outbreak persons with ease.";
	say "     Of course, whether or not these latest additions to your collection will have the same lovely transformative effects as your suit remains to be seen, some clinical side of you waxes. Perhaps you should try them out and find out before you retrieve the head? Who knows, you might enjoy the rush, or find some new exotic mix of species you might favor on the side. If not, there are still plenty of other infections and forms to explore, though you doubt any will be as pretty as your [italic type]snuggly[roman type] foxy form. You hum, stashing away your finds for later.";
	ItemLoss Cardboard Box by 1;
	ItemGain Foxy Paws by 1;
	ItemGain Cute Tail by 1;


