		say "     In the many hours since your strange transformation, your suit has gone oddly still, and with its sudden calm, the vivid fantasies that once nipped at the back of your seems to have abated. Yet, for whatever reason, some part of you feels, you pause searching for the word... cheated by the preternatural torpor of your lovely little costume. You grumble, absentmindedly running your mitts through the silky faux-fuz swaddling your [bodyname of player] form. strange as it may be, you can't help but hope on some level that your fetching trophy might have at last given you a proper foxy form of your dreams. For the joy it might bring you to adopt one of the more common foxy forms filling the city, it still feels like you'd be lowering yourself to becoming one of ubiquitous latex currs wandering the city, or boring fennecs mindlessly prowling the dry plains. Then again, you opine with a disheartened shake of your head, it's not like you can expect the nanites to cater to every whim and provide with such vulpine majesty. Perhaps, some clinical section of your psyche notes, whatever unusual nanites, or unknowable energies that brought forth your latest changes were simply expended in your blissful daydream.";
		say "     Although as you think back on your excursion to the High Rise District, you recall that, according to the shipping documents, your prize was scattered between several distribution sites around the city. True, you have no way of knowing if the remaining pieces are still there, much intact, or, more pertinently, possessed with the same transformative properties as your current attire. Spoiled for time as you sometimes are though, it might be worth a look regardless, who knows what manner of supplies and materials could be left fallow at these shipping hubs. Conversely, a cautionary side of you notes, such places were surely picked over during the early days of the outbreak. What's more, considering the intense nature of your daydreams, is it truly wise to seek out the rest of this unusual costume? You think to yourself, recalling the all too real feelings, and profound sense of dissociation brought on by your fantasies. Then again, a prize such as this could be useful to the right person, so it might be worth seeking out the remaining pieces if only to sell it later.";
		LineBreak;
