					say "     Your body kept ripe and full of beautiful kits by your chosen mates, while you wile away your days in motherly serenity surrounded by your loved ones. Or getting to share those brief, but oh-so-precious moments with your brood when they drink their first meal and grow into comely vixens and strapping tods. True, there is no guarantee your suit is capable of such things, but the chance alone is worth the risk. Besides, even if your form is imperfect, you can mix and match other infections into your own till you achieve the splendor you, and your kits deserve. You ruminate, as you almost regretfully withdrawing your mitt from the supple swell of your cuddly tum, before waddling over to the convenient patch of open ground then sit yourself down with a content sigh and begin digging though your inventory. Though it takes a while as you often find yourself pausing to pamper the lush swell of your snuggable bump, or describe some of your more interesting finds to your lovely kits. You eventually find the folded up slip of paper detailing the drop offs for the suit's remaining pieces.";
					WaitLineBreak;
					say "     The paws and tail it seems were sent to THe Warehouse District to some minor fly-by-night company you've never heard of called: '[bold type]Flying Fuxi's[roman type]' while the head was shipped to, you pause to squint at the crease in the parchment struggling to make out the surviving letters... '[italic type]F*d-U* *xp*e**[roman type].' Darn it, how are you going to find this thing! You hiss grumply under your breath, unable to make heads or tails of the name, much less the address. Unless, Fuxi's has another copy of the shipping bill! You exclaim, in giddy delight. Of course, you'll still need to find it in the twisting maze of derelict storehouses, abandoned buildings, and unsavory establishments dotting the warehouse district, but at least it's a start you think to yourself. Already daydreaming about how nice it will be to have a nice soft set of [italic type]snuggly wuggly[roman type] shoes to strut around in. Or better yet, you hum, idly flexing your [bodyname of player] toes, perhaps gaining some cute foxy paws all your own.";
