				say "pawbs drifting to the cute fluffy curves of your plush kit factory as you thoughtlessly rest your arms along the welcoming swell of your cuddly tumby while you carry on another one-sided conversation with your precious cubs about who they'd like for dinner tonight. Spoiled for choice as you are, it can be quite hard to make up your mind, especially when there are so many yummy ferals running around. You muse, licking your lips as thoughts of stalking some strapping Alpha Wolf in the Urban Forest simmering through your mental landscape, as you picture yourself pinning one those big hunky brutes under the weight of your fox tum while you ride his nice fat knot. Lost to his own personal elysium, the look of simpleminded joy written on your prey face is as priceless as he laps his soft puppy tongue along at your cute little treasure trail, worshiping your glorious brood blessed body in blissful ignorance. You can almost feel the last fleeting twitch of his sculpted meat gracing your nice tight cunt as he cums, basking your hunger folds in a peerless sheen of puppy batter.";
				say "     Followed by the sumptuous look of terror on his muzzle as you lean in, vulpine maw agape as you swallow him whole, reveling in their rich phantom sapor and the raw bestial majesty of their ripped muscles core playing across your palette as you draw them in with praticed ease. All the while, your body ripples with his parting thrashes as you tummy churn him into nice nutritious goop for your cub, or warm, fatty cream for your tits. You ruminate, kits wriggling in shared delight as you massage their quickening forms. Mh, such eager preds, don't worry mommy will get us something soon you hum, giving them a loving pat, which seems to calm them, for the moment at least. But first, you add through a slight inpatient growl as you stare back at your fake tail bobbing you, she needs to get changed first. It shouldn't be long though, your suit only seems to need a day or so to 'recharge', you think to yourself, giving your [TailName of Player] flanks a cheerful shake while you watch the fetching tail dragger bob behind you.";
			else if Dexterity of Mistress Snuggle is 1 and "Vore Predator" is listed in feats of Player:
				say "paws roaming the tight curves of your toned kit-laden tum as you meander through another one-way chat with your brood as you discuss what manner of delicious feral you have for dinner. Perhaps one of those adorable blue gryphons might make a tasty multi-course meal, you tease, smacking your lips at though enjoying a creamy appetizer with your little ones. As images of stacked avian hybrids cuddled in your regal embrace dances through your head. You can almost taste the strange tang of their milk lavishing your taste buds, and feel the warmth of their fur and feathers waltzing along chiseled core as you drink. While their phantom tongue lols from the side of their mouth as you shamelessly grind the silky swell of your ravenous middle along their yummy knot dick as your kits wriggle excitedly within. Soon enough, their vapid expression turn to one of primordial horror as you loom forward, mouth stretched impossibly wide as you engulf their head, then rear back, swallowing them whole in a single motion.";
				say "     Distantly, you can already feel your budding huntresses['] squirm with mutual satisfaction at their unique hybrid sapor of your prey filters across your tongue and exotic interplay of fur and feather tricking your throat while your tummy swells with the welcome weight of your meal. All the while, your tummy fur grows taut as your belly spills over your lap in lovely dome of predatory excess, mentally gushing at the thought, you can't help but taunt your prey thing as your body's potent acid breaking it down in delectable goop for your brood and fuel for your muscles. As its every thrash and panicked screech only serves to excite you and all the further while you paw at your hungry tum. Don't little ones, mommy will find you a yummy meal once she's done changing, you purr, tracing a nail along their exuberant forms. Settling beneath your loving caress, your middle soon goes still and you turn your attention to the fake tail bobbing you. It shouldn't be long though, for your suit only seems to need a day or so to 'recharge', you think to yourself, giving your [TailName of Player] flanks a cheerful shake, watching the fetching floor dragger tail bob behind you.";
			else if bodyname of Player is "Snuggle Fox" and Dexterity of Mistress Snuggle is 1 and "Vore Predator" is not listed in feats of Player:
				say "mitts explore the tender curves of your suit swaddled tumby in eager anticipation of the changes to come as you gab away with your sleepy brood, as the lot of you debate what manner of feral you should treat yourselves to today. Perhaps you might try a nice cuddly goo girl, you ask, resting the weight of your cute little vixens in the palm of your hands. After all, it could be nice to sink into some goop plaything and let her fill your needy holes to the brim with warm, soft slime, you think to yourself. Picturing yourself floating atop some ooze's cushy body while she worships your hale figure. You can almost feel the heady kiss of her morphic body filling your folds, and the blissful squirming of your slutty kits kicking in shared delight as the phantom ooze gleefully massages your lush cunt with the unearthly touch of innumerable pseudopods cascading along your walls in unbound tide.";
				say "     Swooning at the intoxicating fantasy and lovely little wriggle of your naughty monsters playing along your mitts, you nearly consider heading off to the sewers to find yourself such a wondrous playmate, yet think better off, for the moment. After all, you'd like to maintain this form for a while longer and sooner or later, your suit should 'wake up' again, you muse, reasoning it's already been a day or so since its last bout of activity. You wouldn't want to ruin the fun by blighting yours and kits blossoming foxyness with some no-name feral's yucky nanites. You quip, loving drumming your finger padded tum. Tummy gurgling in agreement, your cubs paw at your fingers as they slowly go still. Thought so, but don't worry once mommy is done getting ready we can have the fun we want, you coo booping one of their adorable paws, before turning your attention to the fake tail bobbing you. Just a little longer and this thing should 'recharge', you think to yourself, giving your [TailName of Player] flanks a cheerful shake while you watch the fetching tail dragger bob behind you.";
			if bodyname of Player is "Snuggle Fox" and Perception of Mistress Snuggle is 1 and "Vore Predator" is not listed in feats of Player:
				say "cushy padded mitts exploring the ripe dome of cuddly tummy in quiet admiration of your changes, before resting your arms along its lovely pillowy swell as exuberantly debate with your [italic type]snuggly[roman type] kits what manner of feral you should play with today. Maybe a big fluffy Margay could make for a nice partner, you proffer tracing a gloved finger along your hidden treasure trail. You can only imagine how blissful it would feel to let your arms sink between the soft rows of kitties titties, while the warm kiss of her plush tumby presses against yours. Or share the creamy taste of her milk with your cubs as the two of you relax in each other's arms, you muse, kits squirming at the thought. Mh, glad you naughty widdle vixens approve, you preen, delighting at the rich flood of motherly hormones coursing though you as their sweet pawbs flicker across your palms.";
				say "     Perhaps we should head down to the Fair then? You tease with a playful trill, letting your fingers glide down the cushy curves for your precious suit. Why just think of all the tasty snacks they might have, you pant, thin streaks of drool beading from your lips at the thought of glutting yourself on a few bags of overpriced candy or experimenting with a deep fat frier. After all, you and your babies deserve a treat every now and then. And just think of all the, you pause at the ambient caress of the faux fur serenading your scenes as your mitts explore your [bodyname of Player] legs. Cute cuddly ferals we can play with, you swoon at the thought of riding some nice bouncy rubber tigress's muzzle, or sinking into the welcoming embrace of one of the adorable teddy bears. Of course that may have to wait just a while longer, as you wouldn't want to taint your growing foxiness with some lesser strain. At least not until your suit has a chance to finish changing you and your sweet kits have a chance bloom into proper vixens, you ruminate with cheerful anticipation at the thought of finally getting to hold your fuzzy littler in your arms.";
				WaitLineBreak;
				say "     Your mind is flooded with tender images of your kits nestled to your soft cuddly breast while they take in their first meal, while they look at you with warmth and affection suckle and grow into proper cuddle vixens just like their slutty foxy mommy. You gush, feeling your tummy rumble as faint impressions of their paws dance across its plush padded curves while your eyes drifts back towards the voluminous tail bobbing behind. It shouldn't be long be until suit has fully 'recharged', after it only seems to take a day or so for whatever strange creatures nesting within it awaken from their  exotic toper, you think to yourself, giving your [TailName of Player] flanks a cheerful shake, watching the fetching floor dragger bob behind you.";
		else:
			say "     Thoughtlessly ambling along some desolate stretch of the city, you find your attention drifting towards the soft fluffy floor dragger bobbing behind you as you walk. Wondering all the while how long it will be before your suit wakes up again, from experience, you surmise the thing seems to need just a little over a day before the unusual annelids nesting within are roused from their torpor. Why though, you can't be certain, as they don't seem to require any manner of substances or stimulation to work their magic on your blossoming foxy body. Perhaps they just like making you wait, you opine, idly running a gloved mitt over their supple padding for your precious suit, though for all you know they simply feed on the emotions of yourself and others like some kind of squiggly vampire. Whatever the case hopefully, it shouldn't be much longer now, you muse, giving your [bodyname of Player] hips a mirthful shake, watching it bob behind you as the light seems dance across its silky length like shimmering diamonds upon its fetching reddish orange surface."; [merge here]
		say "      Observing its bounces with a simply goofy grin, you begin to feel a slight, yet-oh-so familiar tingle roiling across your hide like a silky feather was being traced along your spine by some cheeky lover. Oh [']bout time, you murmur contentedly at the first fleeting caress of your costume's coiling tendrils emerging from their homes along your spine. Quizzically, they seem less, you hesitate as a mix of fright and melancholy nip at the back of your mind, exuberant than before as their once frollicking caress seems sluggish and labored as they struggle to slip free of your suit's seam. Perhaps, some analytical side of you posits, whatever force was animating them is being drained each time they change you? If so, then these sweet creatures might be giving everything they have to help you transform, you ruminate, cupping your gloved mitts about their weary forms as you give voice to these sobering thoughts.";
		WaitLineBreak;
		say "     Though unable to reply with words, you can, on some primal level, sense a tacit acknowledgement and resignation in their touch as you coil about your fingers through the lining of your suit. Saddened, you want to ask if there is something you can do to help them, yet think better of it as you can feel motes of resolve bubbling through you as they hug your fingers. These loving beings seem committed to their task of changing you, and you doubt that nothing short of sealing them away will dissuade them from the course they've chosen. Instead, you offer them a grateful smile and a few kind words in appreciation of their work, before relaxing ever-so-slightly into their touch. Wriggling happily in reply, they tenderly hug your fingers once more before encircling your [TailName of Player] flanks in a supple ball of squiggly affection as the latent foxy nanites nestled within you start to stir, "; [Note: the tentacles will not die at the end of this event if the PC chooses to 'merge' with their suit.]
		if bodyname of player is "Snuggle Fox" and Dexterity of Mistress Snuggle is 1:
			say "your lean foxy body thrums in rapturous delight as your toned body seems to drink in the feeler ardent offering.";
			say "    Fresh, toned, sculpted muscle flickers across your athletic, as core middle hardens by the moment with raw primeval sinew, you can't resist running your gloved mitts along your torso, basking in the blossoming border of the potent six packs greeting your curious digits. Smicking, you languidly draw your nails along your burgeoning yummy gutter as the vulpine spread through you, scourging the lingering taint of any lesser strains from your glorious form as the bestial prefection spreads outwards by the second. Coating your regal being in thick, yet comely muscle that's just barely noticeable through the downy padding of your suit. Amazing, you little guys really know how to treat a girl, you yip, flexing your digi legs, exalting at the pleasant creak of the elastic fabric as it stains all the more against the plush cuddly confines of your costume. A faint nascent pressure builds along your tail bone as your fur and flesh bulge outwards.";
			now Dexterity of Mistress Snuggle is 2;
			WaitLineBreak;
		else if bodyname of Player is "Snuggle Fox" and Perception of Mistress Snuggle is 1:
			say "your cuddly mummy tumby rumbles in ravenous elation as your blushing body basks in the velvety wave of change passing through you.";
			say "      As your paws drift back to the lovely swell of your cute foxy belly as the silky layer of supple protective adipose across your ripe middle deepens by the second, another you might have found the extra weight off putting. Yet groping a plush pawful of soft foxy fluff spreading across your gorgeous body like a heavy comforter, some part of you can help but enjoy the growing richness greeting your pads while your gloved mitts slip between the warm, welcoming folds of your blushing kit factory. Mh bet the cubs will love this, you hum, pinching a few silky ";
			if "Touched by Madness" is listed in feats of Player:
				say "centimeters ";
			else:
				say "inches ";
			say "of luxurious furry tallow between your fingers as tender thoughts of your adorable little kits snoozing away in pure comfort within you. You muse, picturing your flush body nestled atop a pillowy throne like some primeval fertility goddess while countless canine attendants pamper your regal form, hand feeding you finest vittles, or the sweetest drinks.";
			WaitLineBreak;
			say "     All the while, your mitts glide down the thickening curves of your doughy thighs as the rapturous blanket of cuddly fluff laced with a hidden core of potent muscle creeps down your bestial legs. Raw, heavy, and more than just a little powerful, your limbs seem to bristle with untapped energy as they strain delectably against the lush lining of your suit. You find it hard to not flex your animalist calves in base contentment, delighting at the thought of wrapping your legs around some yummy treat's muzzle while they worship your plush folds. Or feeling the enticing quiver of your velvety pelt gently rub gently rubbing against itself while the very ground beneath you trembles with every step. Swooing at the image and enthralling feeling of toasty vulpine padding simmering down your legs, you soon find yourself yipping for more. As the soothing coating of spreads across outward across your in arms, though the changes are more subdued than those coiling about your legs, the strange bliss flowing through them is no less addictive as turgid muscle cloaked in the softest pudge billows across your extremities in fetching layer of motherly padding. Gods, you guys know how to treat a girl, you moan, a faint pressure builds along your tail bone as your fur and flesh bulge outwards.";
			now Perception of Mistress Snuggle is 2;
		else:
			say "your [bodydesc of Player] body seems to ripple and convulse beneath oddly rough touch of the struggling feelers playing across your [bodytype of Player] core.";
			say "      At some other juncture, you might have chastised the otherworldly annelids for brutish pinches, or harsh gropes playing across your [TailName of Player] flanks, yet as a charitable side of your notes, the poor tired things must be upset at your lack of appreciation for their work. Though such thoughts to do little placate the mild lancets of discomfort swirling across you, while biting sweet smelling steam pours through the folds of your prize as your body slowly shifts back into the ";
			if Perception of Mistress Snuggle >= 1:
				say "sensual image of matronly mommy fox. ";
			if Dexterity of Mistress Snuggle >= 2:
				say "regal form of a proud vixen. ";
			say "Still, the biting heat of the unearthly vapor sizzle the vulnerable flesh about your vitals and sudden constriction of your costume along your extremities evokes a plaintive vulpine hiss from your [facename of Player] lips while you give voice to your unease. Though slow to respond, the feelers relent, somewhat as the change seeps down through limbs while they're reshaped into their proper foxy forms. Murmuring some vague thanks, and nebulous apology for failing to maintain your shape, you slowly turn your attention to a faint pressure builds along your tail bone as your fur and flesh bulge outwards."; [Merge here]
			setmonster "Snuggle Fox";
			choose row MonsterID from Table of Random Critters;
			now SkinName of Player is Name entry;
			now Skin of Player is skin entry;
			now BodyName of Player is Name entry;
			now Body of Player is body entry;
		say "     Your fuzzy hide parts like the petal of some crimson blossom as bestial bone and wiry sinew presses against the tepid slippery forms of the waning tendrils. Distantly, you can feel sensation filtering outwards along its nascent lengths as your tail-to-be slip edges of your [bodydesc of player] leg while itchiness coils about it. Idly flexing its length, a rich dusting of the same velvety reddish-orange fur coating your foxy figure cascades down its willowy contours you can't help but remark at how... natural it feels. True, you might have experimented with similar transformations in the past, but this feels different, as if your tail were merely asleep, and now beneath the endearing caress of these wondrous tendrils is it finally awake. You muse, slipping your paws about the ";
		if Perception of Mistress Snuggle >= 1:
			say "plump swell of your widening hips ";
		if Dexterity of Mistress Snuggle >= 1:
			say "chiseled curves of your athletic ass ";
		say "as the labored wriggles of your suit born feelers begin to slacken while their slippery surfaces begin to cool. Alarm flare through your mind as, one-by-one, stillness claims them as they go limb, dangling about your thighs akin to desiccate worms while you shout and jostle their perplexingly slender forms, desperately trying to coax some sign of life from them.";
		WaitLineBreak;
		say "     Slowly, almost agonizingly so, they start to respond, tenderly wrapping their temperate from about your foxy finger tips, concern pours out of you as you nearly plead with these kindly beings for answers about what happened to them. Silent as ever, the things seem to sense your distress while they soothingly wriggle about your core, before drawing your hand to the base of your tail like eager children begging their parent's attention. Confused, but in mood to deny them, you let them lead your mitts to your tail bone as you stroke the unsubtle impression of your nascent limb peeking through the dense padding of their home in raw admiration of their work. Before repeating your query to them once in the vein, foolhardy hope that they might assuage the unease bubbling inside you, to no avail. As you can sense, the weakness in their touch, and minute but noticeable loss of mass following your latest change, that these entities will likely not survive your final transformation.";
		say "     Though saddened by the thought, faint bubbles of resolve and pride still ripple through their touch as they fawn over their work while they await your approval. Choked for words, you simply heap praise on them, though some facet of your mind bemoans the notion that these beings seem to be burning themselves at both ends to help you, you just can't bring yourself to deny them their chosen purpose. You grumble, while an oh-so-familier torpor creeps over these spent loyal creatures forms as they retract once more into whatever downy warrens are nestled deep within your suit's lining. Curiously tracing their path with your gloved mitts, it's hard to say where they're going, much less how they seem to be able to vanish inside the down swaddling you, yet they seem to be vaguely nesting along the curves of your suit's middle and base of your spine. Not that such knowledge will do you, or them any good, still as they fade into the cushy stuffing, you nevertheless give them an appreciative pat, before whipping out the shipping records you've collected over the course of journay.";
		WaitLineBreak;
		say "      Skimming though its pointlessly dense job script, you find the address tucked away at the end of long list of lay over and hands off, from what you can gleam, there is a small delivery locker owned by Fed-Up Express on Northwest 7th street tucked within some pop up store you've never heard of. Doubling checking the remaining document to make sure you've got the right address, or haven't missed anything, you soon locate the locker's number: Seven of Nine, along with its password: tertiary adjunct zero tucked into the margins. Shrugging at the odd choice, you nevertheless pocket the pages once more as you collect yourself for the last leg of this impromptu fetch quest. Hopefully, you muse, absentmindedly stroking the faux fur swaddling you, the head will still be there by the time you arrive. After all, you seriously doubt the ferals, not to mention any fellow survivors would have much of any interest in something as frivolous as a furry fox head. Still, there is only one way to find out, you muse, resolving to check 7th street the next time you're in the area.";
		setmonster "Snuggle Fox";
		choose row MonsterID from Table of Random Critters;
		now SkinName of Player is Name entry;
		now Skin of Player is skin entry;
		now BodyName of Player is Name entry;
		now Body of Player is body entry;
		now TailName of Player is Name entry;
		now Tail of Player is Tail entry;
		now HP of Mistress Snuggle is 7;
		if Dexterity of Mistress Snuggle is 2:
			StatChange "Dexterity" by 1;
			StatChange "Strength" by 1;
		else if Perception of Mistress Snuggle is 2:
			StatChange "Stamina" by 1;
			StatChange "Strength" by 1;
		now ScaleValue of Player is 3;


